value.name: Akina Nakamori TRUE LIVE
value.overview:
1993.

A special live performance was held on December 16th, 1995 at Pacifico Yokohama National Hall to coincide with the release of her best album "True Album Akina 95 Best" amidst new challenges, including changing record companies and starting her own agency.

Her signature songs are performed with a band sound, and her sophisticated stage costumes are also impressive, concentrating on her commitment to her live performances.

December 16th, 1995 | Pacifico Yokohama National Hall, Kanagawa
